1
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,800
WOMAN:
I hope you don't mind
decaf, Father.

2
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:10,200
It's all we had
in the cupboard.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,900
A night this cold, I'll
take whatever I can get.

4
00:00:13,900 --> 00:00:16,300
Colleen's upstairs
when you're ready.

5
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:26,200
Colleen?

6
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,100
Colleen, it's me.

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,100
It's all right!

8
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,900
Colleen, it's only me.

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,500
I'm here to pray
with you.

10
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:48,200
F-Father?

11
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:55,200
Oh, Father,
I'm so sorry.

12
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,400
I-I didn't realize...

13
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,300
It's all right,
my child.

14
00:00:58,300 --> 00:01:02,000
No, no, no, no,
it isn't all right.

15
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,900
You're His emissary,
and I-I tried to hurt you.

16
00:01:03,900 --> 00:01:05,200
I-I need to make it up to you.

17
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:08,800
I need to make it up to Him.

18
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:09,900
I can hurt myself!

19
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:11,700
Please don't, Colleen.

20
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:15,500
He doesn't want that,
and neither do I.

21
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,500
Michael, Michael
buys them for me.

22
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,700
Mother doesn't know.

23
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,200
She doesn't like me to have candy,

24
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,800
because
she thinks the sugar excites me,

25
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,800
but Michael knows
they make me happy.

26
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,400
He let's me have two a day.

27
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,600
He counts them every day
to make sure that's all I have,

28
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:38,700
but I've only had one today,
Father,

29
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,500
and I want you
to have the other.

30
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:49,300
Hail Mary full of grace,

31
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:50,200
the Lord is with thee.

32
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,600
Blessed art thou among women

33
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,500
and blessed is the fruit
of thy womb, Jesus.

34
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:56,100
Holy Mary, Mother of God,
pray for our sinners now

35
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,700
and at the hour of our death.

36
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:58,600
Amen.

37
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,100
Hail Mary, full of grace...

